fields.description:
When you create a new user using user preferences different than the defaults, the new values are not saved in the DB.

Preferences in the Admin screen ("new_comment" is false)

{:notifications=>{:added_to_story=>true, :new_comment=>false, :new_discussion=>true}}

Preferences from the DB (all of them are true - which is incorrect, we should see "new comment" as false):
"preferences":{
"notifications":{
"addedToStory":true,
"newComment":true,
"newDiscussion":true
}
